'EXEC NEWUNDO' TO RESTORE ANAPPLESOFT  PROGRAM THAT WAS ERASEDWITH 'NEW' OR   'FP'.  SAVE ANDRELOAD THE PROGRAM      IMMEDIATELYAFTER RESTORING IT TO RESET THEAPPLESOFT POINTERS CORRECTLY.'NEWUNDO.CREATE' CREATES THE'NEWUNDO'  TEXT FILE.SEE ALSO 'UNNEW' ON THE 1984 DISK OFNIBBLE ONE-LINERS.